<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
  <main class="w-2/3 pr-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">SQL Injection 방어 버전</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Prepared Statement(플레이스홀더) 사용</p>
      <form action="/lesson/sql_secure/query" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <label class="block text-gray-700">
          사용자 ID:
          <input
            name="id"
            type="text"
            value="<%= id %>"
            placeholder="예: 1 (숫자만)"
            required
            class="w-full mt-1 px-4 py-2 border rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring"
          />
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition"
        >
          안전 조회
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        입력값이 무조건 플레이스홀더로 바인딩되어<br/>
        SQL Injection 이 완전히 방어됩니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <aside class="w-1/3 pl-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">실사용 SQL</h3>
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-sm">
SELECT *
  FROM users
 WHERE id = ?;
      </pre>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>